    rationale_source: case_law
    requirement_id: REQ-labor-and-employment-law.restrictive-covenant-agreement.tennessee.keep-covenants-within-the-reasonableness-test
    default_value_rationale: >-
      Tied to the employee's actual service area. Geography stays a common-law
      question even after the 2026 statute: the ultimate test is whether the
      territorial limits are greater than required to protect the employer's
      business interest, so a footprint drawn to where the employee actually
      worked or served customers is far easier to defend than one drawn from
      corporate ambition.
  - name: competitive_business_definition
